  <brief_title>Comparison of Two Electroencephalogram (EEG)-Derived Indices With Electroencephalogram Signals</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Bispectral Index and Entropy With Electroencephalogram During Sevoflurane Anaesthesia</official_title>
